.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F000103_9127bc51846b9cce8962c118e35a8e68.jpg&h=28a76983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/013457_bc82aa6ffd4ccfb25c3f707950f21998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F013457_bc82aa6ffd4ccfb25c3f707950f21998.jpg&h=6a44f022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/013500_967e0628782fbb95708f12d06b2a71ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F013500_967e0628782fbb95708f12d06b2a71ed.jpg&h=f2a2f35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/013503_672fdcd893238d152f90b005a4ce1546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F013503_672fdcd893238d152f90b005a4ce1546.jpg&h=7871f3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/013506_bf25add82a181d74f9665a911fbb620d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F013506_bf25add82a181d74f9665a911fbb620d.jpg&h=46baa0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nQ：洗唔洗首抽？<br />\nA：無首抽呢樣野，佢送個D係英雄卷可以直接揀(除左新英)！<br />\n<br />\nQ：咁邊隻英最勁？<br />\nA：其實呢都係玩組合嘅，每一版每隻英強度都會變，<br />\n但我建議你揀樣黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為樣是一世的<br />\n<br />\nQ：D武器點搞啊？點撚樣分？好撚亂啊<br />\nA：專武T10(得武器有專武)<br />\n黃(通常打RAID出)<br />\n紅(打RAID/商店金抽/鑽抽)<br />\n紫(打主線HARD MODE/商店金抽/鑽抽)<br />\n藍(用黎分解)<br />\n綠白(用黎分解)<br />\nBy湯丸<br />\n<br />\nQ：打打下成日卡關，係咪啲英屎？<br />\nA：試下轉手動，升下啲裝就ok架啦<br />\n<br />\nQ：有冇公會？<br />\nA：有就有，不過長期爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等我地公會升左lv就會多返啲人數，各位巴打記住moon po<br />\n公會名：Lihkg<br />\nQ：咁撚多野記點撚柒玩呀？<br />\nA：ching放心，有咩唔明隨便問，唔洗你記呀柒頭<br />\n仲唔快啲玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>送嘅自選2星、3星卷，如下</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/194259_1d637b49403939eb1695c3a88dcea149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F194259_1d637b49403939eb1695c3a88dcea149.jpg&h=214d1bb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>活動5星卷自選卷，可換取角色如下</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">活動到2017年9月30日，即9月24日入坑，每日登齊七日都可以拎到<br />\n每日重置為香港時間為(24小時制)01:00</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011608_d6bc4decba1e267c17c158e2567eee11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011608_d6bc4decba1e267c17c158e2567eee11.jpg&h=9bba54a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011606_c269e86411e2f561cf624184821537f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011606_c269e86411e2f561cf624184821537f0.jpg&h=5859aa3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/up